    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A set of standards proposed by the World Wide Web Consortium to promote common data formats, including a semantic component, in order to convert currently unstructured web documents into a shared framework and a web of data that can be processed by machines. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
